  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enter the world of Everhood</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the color of your soul and what lies beyond the river of death in a strange land. Accompany a mysterious celestial Raven who has deemed you worthy of slaying the Mind Dragon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984020/extras/f0cf13ff18dfcae51f2af00004777a3d.poster.avif?t=1766843514\" width=492 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984020/extras/f0cf13ff18dfcae51f2af00004777a3d.webm?t=1766843514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984020/extras/f0cf13ff18dfcae51f2af00004777a3d.mp4?t=1766843514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the music-based battles with over 100 songs!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voyage through a transcendental journey across 10-12 hours </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter a wild universe with mind-bending visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer the unconquerable</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom World & Battle Editor Support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make funny friends!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984020/extras/69a757ee74fa1340291adea8c58b4589.poster.avif?t=1766843514\" width=578 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1984020/extras/69a757ee74fa1340291adea8c58b4589.webm?t=1766843514\" typ